strings.Value: "Am I the only one who finds it strange that Tristian can't tell us anything about life in Kelesh? – On top of the fact that he does not appear to be of native stock."
"Well... he lived in a monastery — that's why he never saw anything. And he mentioned that his parents weren't from around there — hence his appearance."
"He just doesn't like talking about himself. There's nothing strange in it."
"Does he have anything to say at all, except about his Sarenrae?"
"I'd like to ask him in detail about who he is and where he's from... But on the other hand, no – I've no interest in speaking with him at all."
